 Configuring locale
 &lt;a href="#configuring-locale" class="link icon"&gt;
 &lt;svg&gt;
 &lt;use xlink:href="#anchor-link"&gt;&lt;/use&gt;
 &lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Based on &lt;a href="https://gist.github.com/ChrisTitusTech/f55e2fd0b39b268fed251d12bd91b5e8"&gt;Chris Titus Gist&lt;/a&gt; but changed for GB&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;echo &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;LC_ALL=en_GB.UTF-8&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; | sudo tee -a /etc/environment
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;echo &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;en_GB.UTF-8 UTF-8&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; | sudo tee -a /etc/locale.gen
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;echo &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;LANG=en_GB.UTF-8&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; | sudo tee -a /etc/locale.conf
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo locale-gen en_GB.UTF-8
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Configuring firewall with UFW</title><link>https://notes.markridgwell.com/posts/linux/firewall/</link><pubDate>Tue, 11 Apr 2023 18:14:11 +0100</pubDate><guid>https://notes.markridgwell.com/posts/linux/firewall/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="configuring-firewall-with-ufw" class=link_owner&gt;
