 &lt;a href="#fixing-spectable-screenshot-issues-on-wayland" class="link icon"&gt;
 &lt;svg&gt;
 &lt;use xlink:href="#anchor-link"&gt;&lt;/use&gt;
 &lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id="cant-take-screenshot-with-spectacle" class=link_owner&gt;
 Can&amp;rsquo;t take screenshot with Spectacle
 &lt;a href="#cant-take-screenshot-with-spectacle" class="link icon"&gt;
 &lt;svg&gt;
