 &lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;Screenshot request failed: &amp;#34;The process is not authorized to take a screenshot&amp;#34;
qt.qpa.wayland: Wayland does not support QWindow::requestActivate()
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;fix:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;rm ~/.local/share/applications/org.kde.spectacle.desktop
