 &lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;logotate.conf&lt;/code&gt; by default is set up to rotate logs once a week and keep for 4 weeks. Compression isn&amp;rsquo;t enabled by
default. This doesn&amp;rsquo;t work well with small disks with services that are verbose with what is logged. This sets the
default configuration so that it is better suited.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;note that per service configurations in /etc/logrotate.d/ may also need adjusting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href="https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Logrotate"&gt;ArchWiki&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;note using a file 01-defaults in &lt;code&gt;logrotate.d&lt;/code&gt; means that don&amp;rsquo;t need to worry about updates rewriting the &lt;code&gt;logrotate.conf&lt;/code&gt; file&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Correcting keyboard layout</title><link>https://notes.markridgwell.com/posts/linux/keyboard-layout/</link><pubDate>Fri, 20 Jan 2023 08:47:11 +0100</pubDate><guid>https://notes.markridgwell.com/posts/linux/keyboard-layout/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="correct-keyboard-layout" class=link_owner&gt;
 Correct Keyboard layout
 &lt;a href="#correct-keyboard-layout" class="link icon"&gt;
 &lt;svg&gt;
 &lt;use xlink:href="#anchor-link"&gt;&lt;/use&gt;
 &lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://gist.github.com/keckelt/0ba90f8840e2903bfdc54c7e19ad4613"&gt;See&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;xmodmap -e &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;keycode 49 = grave&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Dynamic DNS with DDClient</title><link>https://notes.markridgwell.com/posts/linux/dynamic-dns-with-ddclient/</link><pubDate>Wed, 11 May 2022 08:47:11 +0100</pubDate><guid>https://notes.markridgwell.com/posts/linux/dynamic-dns-with-ddclient/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="dynamic-dns-with-ddclient" class=link_owner&gt;
 Dynamic DNS with ddclient
 &lt;a href="#dynamic-dns-with-ddclient" class="link icon"&gt;
 &lt;svg&gt;
 &lt;use xlink:href="#anchor-link"&gt;&lt;/use&gt;
 &lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo apt-get install ddclient libdata-validate-ip-perl libjson-any-perl net-tools
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Edit /etc/ddclient.conf as:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;daemon=1800
syslog=yes
protocol=cloudflare
use=web
web=checkip.dyndns.org/ 6
web-skip=‘IP Address’
ssl=yes
login=&amp;lt;Cloudflare Login&amp;gt;
password=&amp;lt;APIKEY&amp;gt;
zone=example.com
host.example.com
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;Verify config&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo service ddclient status
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo ddclient -query
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo ddclient -daemon&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; -verbose -noquiet
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Enable Service&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo service ddclient status
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="set-hostname" class=link_owner&gt;
 Set Hostname
 &lt;a href="#set-hostname" class="link icon"&gt;
 &lt;svg&gt;
 &lt;use xlink:href="#anchor-link"&gt;&lt;/use&gt;
 &lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo hostnamectl set-hostname whatever.example.com
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>